html
	head
		title File Metadata Microservice
		link(href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css", rel="stylesheet", integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u", crossorigin="anonymous")
		link(rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./public/styles/styles.css")
	body
		.container
			h1 API Basejump - File Metadata Microservice
			blockquote
				ul
					li User story: I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload
					li User story: When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response

			h3 Example usage:
			blockquote
				p upload a file from the upload box at the bottom of this page
				code https://as-file-size.herokuapp.com

			h3 Example output:
			blockquote
				code.
					{
					"name": "2016-01-26.png",
					"size": 258957					
					}

			hr
			.upload-box
				h2 Upload:
				form(action="/fileupload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data")
					input(type="file" name="user-file")
					input(type="submit")